// Y_PW1(i) controls the Y filter for PW1(i), 0 <= i <= 6
// C_W0(i)  controls the Cr/Cb filter for W1(i),  0 <= i <= 6
// C_W1(i)  controls the Cr/Cb filter for W1(i),  0 <= i <= 6
// C_PW0(i) controls the Cr/Cb filter for PW1(i), 0 <= i <= 6
